{"tid":1848482,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【TVB係藍經濟圈之首，必須往死裡打】每日洗版任務 - 危險德國孖人牌！(28 Jan)","createTime":"2020-01-28T13:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T07:00:18.000Z","uid":267969,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"ac0599316b470f1c615625e0e004a7b62e73468d","tid":1848482,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新年透夠未呀？<br />\n透夠繼續打TVB啦<br />\n六叔死咗之後已成黨媒<br />\n所有廣告商嘅marketing 都獲藍絲認證<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁辛苦砌TVB廣告商名單<br />\n希望多啲人睇到</span> <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=1bab9278\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a></strong></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【永久抵制精選@初四】</span></strong></span><br />\n1.派嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  2.請願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  3.推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 4.永久抵制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 互like留言，推上FB留言熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>德國孖人牌</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/ZwillingHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FZwillingHK%2F&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=0afb2512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/ZwillingHK/</a></span></strong><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※留言template</strong></span></span><br />\n<blockquote>無綫新聞，誤導市民。貴公司違反向市民承諾，在無綫電視投放廣告，本人將轉用其他品牌，並永久抵制貴公司，敬請注意。忠實顧客上</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/81532576_542759719914215_7495393650134745088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_eui2=AeHuz5pVCcAx0KEkLklcnD4Kyxz6r63_oeJHxcCqcKrEKtr4gosxFXvg6sHjJvdQ5t9J7mvL6eAHTLEok5R17EanxKVDYpyjqx3W7yIHZxK7zQ&amp;_nc_ohc=1z-eTw66DxkAX9ahbL1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=a77c7edd8731b3e0df4bad4584bdd80a&amp;oe=5E8FF711\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F81532576_542759719914215_7495393650134745088_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_eui2%3DAeHuz5pVCcAx0KEkLklcnD4Kyxz6r63_oeJHxcCqcKrEKtr4gosxFXvg6sHjJvdQ5t9J7mvL6eAHTLEok5R17EanxKVDYpyjqx3W7yIHZxK7zQ%26_nc_ohc%3D1z-eTw66DxkAX9ahbL1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3Da77c7edd8731b3e0df4bad4584bdd80a%26oe%3D5E8FF711&h=baabc3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>講下臭屎</strong></span> <br />\n<blockquote>消委會測試：<br />\n$200國產貨，利過$2000孖人牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n⚠️ 珍惜生命，遠離孖人牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n砍骨刀新買半年，只用左4次<br />\n點知斬條魚都斷，凌空飛起劈中心口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事主險被劏開，死裏逃生<br />\n事過半年，交代都無聲&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n <br />\n[Source]<br />\n10倍價錢唔夠人利 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/37KKGyJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37KKGyJ&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=089b34a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/37KKGyJ</a><br />\n險被劏開 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Qrvz7l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Qrvz7l&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=9a5c1bd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bi